Storyline

Dominic and his crew thought they left the criminal mercenary life
 behind. They defeated an international terrorist named Owen Shaw 
and went their seperate ways. But now, Shaw's brother, Deckard Shaw 
is out killing the crew one by one for revenge. Worse, a Somalian 
terrorist called Jakarde, and a shady government official called 
"Mr. Nobody" are both competing to steal a computer terrorism program 
called God's Eye, that can turn any technological device into a weapon. 
Torretto must reconvene with his team to stop Shaw and retrieve the 
God's Eye program while caught in a power struggle between terrorist 
and the United States government.
